snippet.title: Come Back: Chapter 1 - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
** 🎉 Come Back: Chapter 1 - Definitive Edition is out now on Steam, GameJolt & Itch.io for only $4.99!  🎉 **

Buy now on itch.io: https://team-nolan.itch.io/come-back

See more details and stores on https://www.team-nolan.fr/come-back/
**************************************

Do you really want to discover the upsetting truth?

In the first chapter of this mysterious point'n'click adventure coming very soon, you wake up on a mysterious shore and you'll have to find out why are you here and where's your loved one... 

---------------------------------------------
Come Back - A Short Story by Team NoLan
https://www.team-nolan.fr/
